column17:
you take out your mint green top with brown pants and pair it with The Big Bag Theory Tote - For Women.

\r\n

\r\n\tYou attire is something that isn\u2019t regular formal wear due to the burst of colour but it is not entirely inappropriate either. As soon as you walk into office

column19:
this tote is made for the woman who is restrained yet reckless.

Wear your attitude on your sleeve with this Big Bag Theory Tote – For Women. This tote bag is made of canvas and hence offers sturdy and rigid support to all your possessions while use. The commodious interiors of this Big Bag Theory Tote – For Women comfortably accommodate the everyday essentials and facilitates instant access to the basic items on the go. Measuring 355.6 x 381 mm in dimension
column17: this satchel is absolutely lightweight and is effortless to carry while use. Besides this
column18:
